message.body: Just had the best night with tim.
Had drinks by the river. He talked about Brian! He was like "Martha I never talk about Brian" and we talked about Sarah too
Awww that sounds like our life's mission is complete - breaking through to tim!
Right? I think he's just in a good place though too.
Also, hes been initiating to hang out with me! I didn't even have to dawg him to text me back.... Hah
Kinda like us ;) actually I had a really good weekend and was honest with the rents. Slowly things are feeling better.
Good. Honest about your anxieties? I feel a lot better than last week too.
Yes about a lot of stuff!
